channel.title: PowerScape v5 508!
channel.description:
[size=20pt]PowerScape v5 508![/size]
[size=20pt]NOT CODED YET FOR MOST NPC's[/size]
Features
-All emotes -All skill capes -Training area -Commands -G.E map data -73% spawned lumbridge -100% spawned god wars -All spec attacks -36.7 % skills fully operable (yes that is a real percent that i calculated by doing math!) -HD Supported -Clan chat -Working friends list -Working dual arena (stakes are a bit glitchy) -Working npc drops (except the "Man" NPC) -14% of npc speech works (once again i did real math to get that) -9% of modern spells work -All ancient spells work -Prayer works with normal bones and wolf bones (dragon bones will freeze the client) -G.E not spawned yet -Varrock about 43% or 44% spawned (a rough estimate, didn't have time to calculate) -Kalphite Works! -King Black Dragon Works! -All god armor, god swords, and skill capes are wearable and functional -Large lag handler to eliminate any in game issue which may lag the server (still need a decent connection though) -Basic player commands
